    content: 'Check if we\'re running in your electorate. If yes, put us first on your ballot. Even if we don\'t win your seat, every vote sends a message that Victorians are done with corporate-funded major parties.',
    link: 'https://fusionparty.org.au/electorates',
    linkText: 'Check: fusionparty.org.au/electorates'
  },
  {
