    title: 'Volunteer',
    content: 'This is where movements are won. Door knocking. Phone banking. Market stalls. Organizing. Even a few hours matters. We\'ll train you. You don\'t need experience. You just need to care.',
    link: 'https://fusionparty.org.au/volunteer',
    linkText: 'Sign Up to Volunteer',
    isPrimary: true
  },
  {
    icon: 'üí¨',
    title: 'Spread the Word',
    content: 'Share this manifesto with one person who\'s tired of the major parties. When people complain about housing, transport, healthcare - tell them there\'s an alternative. Use the "they stole it, we\'re taking it back" framing.'
  },
  {
    icon: 'üí∞',
    title: 'Donate',
    content: 'We don\'t take corporate donations. Ever. We\'re funded by people like you. Every dollar goes to the campaign. No consultant fees. No corporate perks.',
    link: 'https://fusionparty.org.au/donate',
    linkText: 'Donate Now'
  },
  {
