---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Get Involved | Join the Reclaim Movement - Fusion Victoria"
  description="Volunteer, donate, spread the word. Every action matters. Join the movement to reclaim Victoria's future."
>
  <Header />
  
  <Hero 
    title="Join The Reclaim Movement"
    subtitle="The future belongs to those who reclaim it. Let's get to work."
  />

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-magenta-light border-l-4 border-magenta p-8 rounded mb-8">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">This isn't about one election. It's about building a movement that forces change, whether we're in government or not.</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-black text-magenta">Every action matters. Every volunteer. Every conversation. Every vote.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>We're not a professional political machine funded by corporations. We're a grassroots movement powered by people who are done with major party bullshit.</p>
        <p>Whether you can volunteer a few hours, donate what you can afford, or just spread the word - you're part of building something bigger.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WAYS TO GET INVOLVED -->
  <section class="bg-light-grey py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-magenta mb-12 text-center">How You Can Help</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {actionItems.map(item => (
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-transparent hover:border-mint transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">{item.icon}</div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-4">{item.title}</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">{item.content}</p>
            {item.link && (
              <a href={item.link} class={`btn ${item.isPrimary ? 'btn-primary' : 'btn-secondary'} inline-block mt-4`}>
                {item.linkText}
              </a>
            )}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VOLUNTEER ROLES -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-magenta mb-12 text-center">What Volunteers Do</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-12">
        {volunteerRoles.map(category => (
          <div class="bg-light-grey p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-4">{category.title}</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {category.roles.map(role => (
                <li>
                  <strong>{role.name}</strong>
                  {role.desc && <span class="text-sm text-gray-600"> - {role.desc}</span>}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="bg-magenta-solid text-white p-8 rounded-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Have Expertise?</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">If you have skills in policy, data, organizing, communications, legal, finance - we need you.</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold">This is a movement built by people who know their stuff. Bring your expertise. Help us build something that works.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXPECTATION SETTING -->
  <section class="bg-light-grey py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-magenta mb-12 text-center">What To Expect</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-magenta mb-6">We Won't Form Government in 2026. We Know That.</h3>
        
        <p class="text-xl mb-4">But every vote we win sends a message. Every seat we contest forces the major parties to explain themselves. Every question we ask in Parliament exposes waste they'd rather hide.</p>
        
        <p class="text-xl mb-4"><strong>The Greens started with one seat in 1996. Now they're kingmakers.</strong> Every movement starts somewhere.</p>
        
        <p class="text-xl">We're building for the long term. But we're also impatient. People are hurting now. So we'll fight like we can win.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-grey-dark text-white p-10 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-mint mb-6">The Part That Might Surprise You</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">We don't care who implements these policies. If Labor reads our manifesto and builds 50,000 public homes - <strong>that's a win</strong>.</p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">If the Liberals cut infrastructure waste and invest in revenue-generating assets - <strong>that's a win</strong>.</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">We're not here to protect intellectual property. We're here to fix Victoria.</p>
        <p class="text-xl">The ideas matter more than who gets credit.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THREE IMMEDIATE ACTIONS -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-magenta mb-12 text-center">Three Things You Can Do Right Now</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-light-grey p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-4">1. Amplify the Message</h4>
          <p class="mb-4">Share this with one person who's tired of major party failures. When the next infrastructure disaster hits, point people here. Use the "they stole it, we're taking it back" framing.</p>
          <a href="/manifesto" class="btn btn-secondary inline-block">Share the Manifesto</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-light-grey p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-4">2. Join the Build</h4>
          <p class="mb-4">Sign up to volunteer - even a few hours matters. If you have expertise (policy, data, organizing), we need you.</p>
          <a href="https://fusionparty.org.au/volunteer" class="btn btn-primary inline-block">Volunteer Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-light-grey p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-4">3. Support the Campaign</h4>
          <p class="mb-4">We don't take corporate money. We're funded by people. Every donation - $5, $50, $500 - keeps us independent.</p>
          <a href="https://fusionparty.org.au/donate" class="btn btn-secondary inline-block">Donate</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT INFO -->
  <section class="bg-light-grey py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-magenta mb-12 text-center">Get In Touch</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üìß</div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-3">Email</h4>
          <p class="mb-2"><a href="mailto:hello@fusionparty.org.au" class="text-magenta hover:underline font-semibold">hello@fusionparty.org.au</a></p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Questions? Ideas? Want to get involved? Email us.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üåê</div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-3">Website</h4>
          <p class="mb-2"><a href="https://fusionparty.org.au" class="text-magenta hover:underline font-semibold">fusionparty.org.au</a></p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Full policy platform, costings, and updates.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üê¶</div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-3">Social Media</h4>
          <p class="mb-2"><a href="https://twitter.com/FusionPartyVic" class="text-magenta hover:underline font-semibold">@FusionPartyVic</a></p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Follow for updates, campaign news, and policy discussions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üìç</div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-magenta mb-3">Find Your Electorate</h4>
          <p class="mb-2">Check if we're running in your area:</p>
          <p><a href="https://fusionparty.org.au/electorates" class="text-magenta hover:underline font-semibold">fusionparty.org.au/electorates</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="bg-magenta-gradient text-white py-20 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8">The Future Won't Be Given To Us. It Must Be Reclaimed.</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-white/10 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-left max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
          <li><strong>50,000 public homes over 4 years</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Melton Line built by 2029</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Universal Basic Income</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Wage theft criminalised</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Infrastructure waste cut by $2.8 billion/year</strong></li>
          <li><strong>State renewables generating $280 million/year</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Debt-to-GSP down to 25%</strong></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p class="text-2xl mb-6">The major parties won't do this. They can't - they're trapped in a system they built to serve their donors, not you.</p>
      
      <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 text-mint">But we can. And with your help, we will.</p>
      
      <div class="cta-buttons mb-12">
        <a href="https://fusionparty.org.au/volunteer" class="btn btn-primary">Volunteer</a>
        <a href="https://fusionparty.org.au/donate" class="btn btn-secondary">Donate</a>
        <a href="/manifesto" class="btn btn-secondary">Read Manifesto</a>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black">Let's Get To Work.</h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
